00:40:39,060 --> 00:40:40,600
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I know that face...</font>

698
00:40:41,020 --> 00:40:45,040
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's the 200-million man from North Blue, Trafalgar Law.</font>

699
00:40:45,880 --> 00:40:48,000
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I heard some bad rumors about him.</font>

