00:41:02,240 --> 00:41:04,420
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We've got something incredible today!</font>

704
00:41:04,660 --> 00:41:07,340
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Today's big draw is a giant, right? I already know.</font>

