00:41:07,520 --> 00:41:10,340
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Leave it to me. I'll be sure to get a good price for him.</font>

706
00:41:10,480 --> 00:41:12,460
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Are the cherry blossoms prepared yet?</font>

707
00:41:12,620 --> 00:41:17,220
