00:43:26,320 --> 00:43:27,840
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Quit pretending.</font>

741
00:43:27,980 --> 00:43:30,480
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">That was you, right? That "Haki" just now.</font>

742
00:43:31,240 --> 00:43:32,820
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Who the hell are you?</font>

